'''Actukn''' gan yat tamunt n tqbilin timaziɣin. llan wactuckn ɣ [[Sus]], tili yat tfult n wacuktn ɣ dukal, ikka tt inn ismatti tt lmxzn. Ibdr tt Ibn Xaldun ɣ tzwart nns mas d tga zɣ tqbilin [[Igzuln|tigzulin]] illan ɣ Sus.

Ɣ 1700, mmattin kra n wactukn zɣ sus s tsga n uzmmur.<ref>''[http://data.bnf.fr/34351154/l_agronomie_coloniale__paris_/ tasnfllaḥt takulunyalt]''. (s tfransist)</ref>

Ɣ umzwaru ɣ yunyu 1913, slmn wactukn n sus i ifransisn.<ref>''abarizi amẓyan'', aynas 2 yunyu 1913. (s tfransist)</ref>

